---
title: Tandoori Cauliflower Bowl with Garlic Rice & Mint Yoghurt
description: Cook a rainbow for dinner with this beautiful tandoori cauliflower bowl! You may not wind up with a pot of gold, but with a tasty assortment of colourful toppings, like our easy tomato salsa and creamy mint yoghurt, you'll feel like a million bucks.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tandoori-cauliflower-bowl-4fc6a7f5.jpg
